post_text:
The magnificent members of our IT Department received a special lunch today!

A big thank you to Hector Hek Valdez and Cesar Flores, local HB residents, for providing a delicious lunch to our IT Department today as a way of saying “thank you” to hardworking essential workers in our community. Our IT Department has been nothing short of amazing during COVID-19 and it was so nice to see these unsung heroes receive this act of kindness. Thanks also to the HB Quarantine Cuisine for donations made to this movement.

@hektattoo #actofkindness #essentialworkers #itdepartment #ovsdrelationshipsmatter #ovsd

